node.text: We’ve always had a soft spot for white bedding. Equal parts versatile and luxurious, it creates a look that feels restful and quiet. ✨ Here, our Oyster Bay Duvet’s little flourish along the trim adds a bit of texture and playfulness, making the look even more dynamic. Plus, it’s now specially priced and ready to ship. #serenaandlily

node.text: Enjoy special pricing on everything you need for a beautiful bedroom, including our Driftway Chest. ✨Handwrapped in linen, this Parsons-style design is a standout in so many ways. To create the nuanced tones, we painted the linen fabric and sanded it down, giving it a slightly weathered finish. The scale is just right – large enough to hold what you need, without overpowering a room. #serenaandlily
